title: [Gyldemar Forest, Overgrown Path]
description: The undergrowth nearly envelopes the pair of oaks that have fallen across the path.  A handful of acorns spill out from a knothole in one of the fallen oaks.

The undergrowth nearly envelopes the pair of oaks that have fallen across the path, appearing like the fallen forms of giants in the nighttime darkness.  A handful of acorns spill out from a knothole in one of the fallen oaks.
